  "message": "\ud83d\udcd6 fix: correct ACMM badge rendering in README (#8979) (#9964)\n\nRemove base64-encoded SVG data URI from the badge URL. GitHub's CSP\nblocks data: URIs in badge images, causing the badge to not render.\nThe badge endpoint already returns namedLogo via its JSON response,\nso removing the custom logo parameter is sufficient.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>",
